        {
            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20it%20about%20praise%20that%20is%20so%20powerful%3F%20Why%20are%20we%20so%20strongly%20exhorted%20in%20so%20many%20scriptures%20to%20praise%20the%20Lord%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EFirst%2C%20praise%20blesses%20God.%20When%20His%20people%20praise%20His%20name%20with%20dancing%20and%20make%20music%20to%20Him%20with%20tambourine%20and%20harp%2C%20the%20Lord%20takes%20delight%20in%20them%20(Psalm%20149%3A4).%20We%20bless%20Him%20when%20we%20dance%2C%20clap%2C%20rejoice%2C%20and%20are%20glad%20in%20Him.%20The%20saints%20should%20ever%20%22rejoice%20in%20his%20honor%22%20and%20%22sing%20for%20joy%20as%20they%20lie%20on%20their%20beds%22%20(v.%205).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESecond%2C%20praise%20engages%20mighty%20warfare%20against%20the%20enemy.%20If%20it%20is%20our%20honor%20to%20praise%20the%20Lord%2C%20then%20it%20is%20our%20glory%20to%20put%20our%20enemies%20to%20flight%20through%20praise%20(v.%209).%20Praise%20has%20the%20power%20%22to%20bind%20their%20kings%20with%20shackles%20and%20their%20leaders%20with%20iron%20chains%22%20(v.%208).%20As%20we%20praise%20God%2C%20the%20sentence%20upon%20our%20enemies%20as%20written%20in%20the%20Word%20of%20God%20is%20executed.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ENever%20underestimate%20the%20power%20of%20praise.%20King%20Hezekiah's%20simple%20worship%20and%20prayer%20brought%20the%20angel%20of%20the%20Lord%20into%20his%20situation.%20In%20one%20night%2C%20the%20angel%20killed%20185%2C000%20Assyrian%20troops%2C%20and%20Judah%20was%20delivered%20from%20the%20enemy's%20hands%20(2%20Kings%2019%3A35).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPraise%20ye%20the%20Lord!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Kgs.18:13-19:37",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Kings%2018%3A13-19%3A37%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAssyria%20Invades%20Judah%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EIn%20the%20fourteenth%20year%20of%20King%20Hezekiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A13%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20fourteenth%20year%20of%20Hezekiah%26%23x2019%3Bs%20reign%20was%20701%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-sc%22%3Eb.c.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20King%20Sennacherib%20of%20Assyria%20came%20to%20attack%20the%20fortified%20towns%20of%20Judah%20and%20conquered%20them.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20Hezekiah%20sent%20this%20message%20to%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%20at%20Lachish%3A%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20have%20done%20wrong.%20I%20will%20pay%20whatever%20tribute%20money%20you%20demand%20if%20you%20will%20only%20withdraw.%26%23x201D%3B%20The%20king%20of%20Assyria%20then%20demanded%20a%20settlement%20of%20more%20than%20eleven%20tons%20of%20silver%20and%20one%20ton%20of%20gold.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A14%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3E300%26%23xA0%3Btalents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B10%26%23xA0%3Bmetric%20tons%5D%20%3Cem%3Eof%20silver%20and%2030%26%23xA0%3Btalents%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B1%26%23xA0%3Bmetric%20ton%5D%20%3Cem%3Eof%20gold.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ETo%20gather%20this%20amount%2C%20King%20Hezekiah%20used%20all%20the%20silver%20stored%20in%20the%20Temple%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20in%20the%20palace%20treasury.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EHezekiah%20even%20stripped%20the%20gold%20from%20the%20doors%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Temple%20and%20from%20the%20doorposts%20he%20had%20overlaid%20with%20gold%2C%20and%20he%20gave%20it%20all%20to%20the%20Assyrian%20king.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%20sent%20his%20commander%20in%20chief%2C%20his%20field%20commander%2C%20and%20his%20chief%20of%20staff%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A17a%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20rabshakeh%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2018%3A19%2C%2026%2C%2027%2C%2028%2C%2037.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20from%20Lachish%20with%20a%20huge%20army%20to%20confront%20King%20Hezekiah%20in%20Jerusalem.%20The%20Assyrians%20took%20up%20a%20position%20beside%20the%20aqueduct%20that%20feeds%20water%20into%20the%20upper%20pool%2C%20near%20the%20road%20leading%20to%20the%20field%20where%20cloth%20is%20washed.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A17b%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Ebleached.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThey%20summoned%20King%20Hezekiah%2C%20but%20the%20king%20sent%20these%20officials%20to%20meet%20with%20them%3A%20Eliakim%20son%20of%20Hilkiah%2C%20the%20palace%20administrator%3B%20Shebna%20the%20court%20secretary%3B%20and%20Joah%20son%20of%20Asaph%2C%20the%20royal%20historian.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ESennacherib%20Threatens%20Jerusalem%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20Assyrian%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20chief%20of%20staff%20told%20them%20to%20give%20this%20message%20to%20Hezekiah%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20great%20king%20of%20Assyria%20says%3A%20What%20are%20you%20trusting%20in%20that%20makes%20you%20so%20confident%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_20%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3EDo%20you%20think%20that%20mere%20words%20can%20substitute%20for%20military%20skill%20and%20strength%3F%20Who%20are%20you%20counting%20on%2C%20that%20you%20have%20rebelled%20against%20me%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_21%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20Egypt%3F%20If%20you%20lean%20on%20Egypt%2C%20it%20will%20be%20like%20a%20reed%20that%20splinters%20beneath%20your%20weight%20and%20pierces%20your%20hand.%20Pharaoh%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Egypt%2C%20is%20completely%20unreliable!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_22%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BBut%20perhaps%20you%20will%20say%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BWe%20are%20trusting%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God!%26%23x2019%3B%20But%20isn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20he%20the%20one%20who%20was%20insulted%20by%20Hezekiah%3F%20Didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20Hezekiah%20tear%20down%20his%20shrines%20and%20altars%20and%20make%20everyone%20in%20Judah%20and%20Jerusalem%20worship%20only%20at%20the%20altar%20here%20in%20Jerusalem%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_23%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BI%26%23x2019%3Bll%20tell%20you%20what!%20Strike%20a%20bargain%20with%20my%20master%2C%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria.%20I%20will%20give%20you%202%2C000%20horses%20if%20you%20can%20find%20that%20many%20men%20to%20ride%20on%20them!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_24%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EWith%20your%20tiny%20army%2C%20how%20can%20you%20think%20of%20challenging%20even%20the%20weakest%20contingent%20of%20my%20master%26%23x2019%3Bs%20troops%2C%20even%20with%20the%20help%20of%20Egypt%26%23x2019%3Bs%20chariots%20and%20charioteers%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_25%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E25%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%26%23x2019%3Bs%20more%2C%20do%20you%20think%20we%20have%20invaded%20your%20land%20without%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20direction%3F%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20himself%20told%20us%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BAttack%20this%20land%20and%20destroy%20it!%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_26%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2226%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E26%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Eliakim%20son%20of%20Hilkiah%2C%20Shebna%2C%20and%20Joah%20said%20to%20the%20Assyrian%20chief%20of%20staff%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BPlease%20speak%20to%20us%20in%20Aramaic%2C%20for%20we%20understand%20it%20well.%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20speak%20in%20Hebrew%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E18%3A26%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ein%20the%20dialect%20of%20Judah%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20in%2018%3A28.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20the%20people%20on%20the%20wall%20will%20hear.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_27%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E27%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Sennacherib%26%23x2019%3Bs%20chief%20of%20staff%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BDo%20you%20think%20my%20master%20sent%20this%20message%20only%20to%20you%20and%20your%20master%3F%20He%20wants%20all%20the%20people%20to%20hear%20it%2C%20for%20when%20we%20put%20this%20city%20under%20siege%2C%20they%20will%20suffer%20along%20with%20you.%20They%20will%20be%20so%20hungry%20and%20thirsty%20that%20they%20will%20eat%20their%20own%20dung%20and%20drink%20their%20own%20urine.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_28%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20chief%20of%20staff%20stood%20and%20shouted%20in%20Hebrew%20to%20the%20people%20on%20the%20wall%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BListen%20to%20this%20message%20from%20the%20great%20king%20of%20Assyria!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_29%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20what%20the%20king%20says%3A%20Don%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20Hezekiah%20deceive%20you.%20He%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20rescue%20you%20from%20my%20power.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_30%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3EDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20let%20him%20fool%20you%20into%20trusting%20in%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20by%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20surely%20rescue%20us.%20This%20city%20will%20never%20fall%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20Assyrian%20king!%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_31%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2231%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E31%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen%20to%20Hezekiah!%20These%20are%20the%20terms%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%20is%20offering%3A%20Make%20peace%20with%20me%26%23x2014%3Bopen%20the%20gates%20and%20come%20out.%20Then%20each%20of%20you%20can%20continue%20eating%20from%20your%20own%20grapevine%20and%20fig%20tree%20and%20drinking%20from%20your%20own%20well.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_32%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2232%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E32%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20I%20will%20arrange%20to%20take%20you%20to%20another%20land%20like%20this%20one%26%23x2014%3Ba%20land%20of%20grain%20and%20new%20wine%2C%20bread%20and%20vineyards%2C%20olive%20groves%20and%20honey.%20Choose%20life%20instead%20of%20death!%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BDon%26%23x2019%3Bt%20listen%20to%20Hezekiah%20when%20he%20tries%20to%20mislead%20you%20by%20saying%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20will%20rescue%20us!%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_33%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2233%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E33%3C%2Fspan%3EHave%20the%20gods%20of%20any%20other%20nations%20ever%20saved%20their%20people%20from%20the%20king%20of%20Assyria%3F%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs2_18_34%22%20bk%3D%22kgs2%22%20ch%3D%2218%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20happened%20to%20the%20gods%20of%20Hamath%20and%20Arpad%3F%20And%20what%20about%20the%20gods%